oji\" />"},{"pid":"9dccd510091b04b045fa7ca91133b1b73f920f56","tid":1680407,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T21:05:14.000Z","msg":"用歷史證明加國係手足，但掉轉黎講，<br />\n又唔當日本係仇人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81ae695ce378f6ff119a2f0e8a25cb324b3b81e","tid":1680407,"uid":26532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T21:08:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98e57825b0d8257cab262d16c5f2c235eccad653","tid":1680407,"uid":335391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T21:12:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c2ab193fe7c3b3ed492ff6c4d8347d095446a3e0","tid":1680407,"uid":195158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dccd510091b04b045fa7ca91133b1b73f920f56","tid":1680407,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T21:05:14.000Z","msg":"用歷史證明加國係手足，但掉轉黎講，<br />\n又唔當日本係仇人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T21:17:42.000Z","msg":"手足逆思得好<br />\n但1945年日本投降後帝國主義亦都落幕...好多國民，例德人日人都唔鍾意重提侵略舊事，但前人犧牲就要紀念。正如他日煲底下都會有烈士嘅位置<br />\n<br />\n同埋大家有眼見今次日媒幾大力幫香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844dacb648da7e47d7987da2a09f4eedb0618bfb","tid":1680407,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T23:37:42.000Z","msg":"有無英文版<br />\n想俾加大拿人睇"},{"pid":"9bb8cfe40e0e1fae900719b81264fdf6605dcc1c","tid":1680407,"uid":195158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"844dacb648da7e47d7987da2a09f4eedb0618bfb","tid":1680407,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T23:37:42.000Z","msg":"有無英文版<br />\n想俾加大拿人睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T23:53:21.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong is an amicable ally o